# Project Rules for Cline

<!-- Auto-generated by hashmark (https://hashmark.md) -->

## Stack: Next.js 16.1.6 + App Router + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS + prisma
143 files, 33 components

## Rules

1. ALWAYS use existing components (33 available). NEVER create duplicates.
2. ALWAYS use semantic design tokens: bg-primary, text-foreground, border-border.
3. NEVER hardcode color values (no bg-blue-500, no #hex, no rgb()).
4. Default to Server Components. Only add 'use client' for interactivity.
5. Use next/image for images and next/link for navigation.
6. Type all function parameters. NEVER use 'any'.
7. Use Tailwind scale values. No arbitrary values like w-[137px].

## Commands

- npm run dev — Start development server
- npm run build — Production build
- npm test — Run tests
- npm run lint — Lint code
- npm run typecheck — Type check
- npm run db:push — Database
- npm run db:generate — Database
- npm run db:studio — Database
- npm run db:seed — Database
- npm run db:search-setup — Database

